     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 20 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20poliovirus|20primary|20series|20doses|20were|20administered-130\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nopoliovirusprimaryseriesdoseswereadministered-130\">No poliovirus primary series doses were administered-130</a></td><td>No poliovirus primary series doses were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Poliovirus-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20less|20than|206|20weeks-40\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageislessthan6weeks-40\">Client's age is less than 6 weeks-40</a></td><td>Client's age is less than 6 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" &lt; 6 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioIPVOnlyVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20not|20due|20for|20IPV|20vaccination-48\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-ClientisnotdueforIPVvaccination-48\">Client is not due for IPV vaccination-48</a>